snippet.title: Fallen Aces - Official Gameplay Video | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description:
Take a look at gameplay in this latest video for Fallen Aces, an upcoming crime noir FPS game. In the gameplay video, we get to see combat and a variety of weapons in action, including a spear gun, fists, a gun, a nail-filled plank of wood, and more. Fallen Aces will be available on PC. The A.C.E.S, watchful guardians of Switchblade City, are being taken down, one by one. Now it's up to one man, with two fists, to get to the bottom of it all.

#IGN #Gaming
